data.description: Investment opportunity on the main road of West Mountain St. near East Forsyth High School. Home's hardwood flooring is solid throughout with easy flow between living, kitchen, and bedrooms. Refrigerator and appliances remain. Roof replaced 2017. Outside features a spaciously sized dog run and back building that will need reworking. What too look out for: No AC or Heat (furnace in place with above ground oil tank, may just need repair) – Debris in some areas which will be removed with acceptable offer. Priced to sell and can serve as an excellent starter/rental home for your inventory. Accepting review of all offers 05-01-24 but will favor any strong offers made prior. Schedule a visit today and see what investment may be yours
